Maintainer: Justin Wilkins <justin.wilkins@occams.com>
Description: Log-likelihood profiling tools for nlmixr2 fits, including
    fixed-value profiling, PsN-style iterative likelihood profiling,
    optional parallel execution, and S3 helpers for intervals, printing,
    and plotting.
